title: Samsung gains help from an old friend for iPhone 14 OLED ‘M12’ material
content:
As iPhone 14 production has reportedly started already, it’s only natural we’re going to hear more details about this upcoming product. Now, a report indicates that Samsung Display is adding a new supplier for the OLED material of the new iPhone.
